| Virtual Scroll | ‚ùå | ‚ö†Ô∏è | ‚ö†Ô∏è | ‚úÖ **CDK Nativo** |
| Fuzzy Search | ‚ùå | ‚ùå | ‚ùå | ‚úÖ **Nativo** |
| Multi-Select Chips | ‚ùå | ‚ö†Ô∏è | ‚úÖ | ‚úÖ **Melhorado** |
